Myles Jeffrey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Myles_Jeffrey 0 Myles David Jeffrey (born October 5, 1990) is an American actor, producer, voice artist, comedian and former child actor. He played Henry Paget on Early Edition and voiced George in Stuart Little.
